end-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T02:10:13Z to 2025-06-20T02:22:13Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 02:10:13+00:00 to 2025-06-20 02:22:13+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["emailservice-1", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "frontend-0", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-1", "cartservice-1", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["currencyservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "frontend-2", "checkoutservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "region_pending", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "从 UUID 为 e1950aec-393 的查询中，我们找到了相关时间段内的错误日志，但没有找到匹配的监控数据和 Trace 数据。以下是日志分析结果：\n\n### 日志分析发现\n- **日志信息**:\n  - 服务名称: `frontend`\n  - 错误消息: `\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"`\n  - 频次:\n    - frontend-2: 56 次\n    - frontend-1: 44 次\n    - frontend-0: 39 次\n\n### 结果分析\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"transport\", \n    \"Error while dialing\", \n    \"lookup shippingservice\", \n    \"server misbehaving\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"DNS issues when trying to connect to shippingservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 评论\n上述日志显示，当 frontend 服务尝试在 checkout 过程中通过 DNS 查找 `shippingservice` 时，发生了一些网络或 DNS 配置错误，导致连接失败。这种情况强烈暗示 DNS 函数或网络配置异常所致。然而，我们也需要获取更多数据，如 Metrics 和 Trace，以进一步确认和解决这个问题。", "trace_analysis_findings": "根据调用链数据分析，以下是异常调用链中的显著延迟和错误情况：\n\n### 延迟分析\n1. **CheckoutService → ShippingService**\n   - 正常平均时长: 9415.74 ms\n   - 异常平均时长: 1698200.23 ms\n   - 延迟倍数: 180\n   - 原因: 网络连接问题 (Transport Error)\n\n2. **Frontend → CheckoutService (PlaceOrder)**\n   - 正常平均时长: 153703.35 ms\n   - 异常平均时长: 1908846.49 ms\n   - 延迟倍数: 12.4\n\n### 错误状态码分析\n- 多个调用链报告 **code = Unavailable** 错误，说明 ShippingService 服务不可用，连接失败。\n- 异常情况多次发生于 CheckoutService 与 ShippingService 的调用链中，涉及的错误信息中提到 DNS 服务器故障。\n\n### 关键发现提取\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal: 9415.74 ms, Anomaly: 1698200.23 ms, Transport Error while dialing\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Unavailable, connection error: DNS server misbehaving\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些发现表明，CheckoutService 和 ShippingService 之间的调用链中出现了显著的网络连接问题，这导致了系统故障。建议重点检查 ShippingService 的可用性及相关网络配置。", "metric_analysis_findings": "在对 UUID `e1950aec-393` 的指标数据分析中，我发现以下显著的异常指标：\n\n### 异常指标提取\n- **error_ratio**: 服务错误率方面，`checkoutservice-1` 的错误率显著上升，变化率达到了 45.22% 的中位数和 48.38% 的 P99。\n- **region_pending**: TiDB 组件 `tidb-tikv` 的 `region_pending` 指标显示异常，P99 变化率为 46.32%。\n\n### 关键发现与假设\n根据异常指标和其变化率，以下是我提出的假设：\n\n1. **Component: `checkoutservice-1`**\n   - **Reason**: `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 指标都有显著的上涨，表明 `checkoutservice-1` 服务在故障期间有大量的错误请求。\n   - **Evidence**: `error_ratio` 从正常中位数的 0.0% 上升到故障中 45.22%，P99 从 0.0% 上升到 48.38%。\n\n2. **Component: `tidb-tikv`**\n   - **Reason**: `region_pending` 指标异常表明 TiDB 层级的瓶颈，影响数据库性能。\n   - **Evidence**: `region_pending` 中位数变化率为 15.9%，P99 为 46.32%，显示显著的性能问题。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"region_pending\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Error ratio and server_error_ratio spikes indicate massive error requests during the fault.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0% to 45.22%, and P99 from 0.0% to 48.38%.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region pending metric shows performance bottleneck at the TiDB layer.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"region_pending median change ratio is 15.9% and P99 is 46.32%.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n我已经提取了上述异常并进行了详细分析，可以帮助进一步深入调查根因。"}
