 shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"e8567e1c-3d73-43da-b6a1-9eb3333f8876\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"8d523130-747f-4687-88d3-cc9658146376\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T02:10:16.888874163Z\"\"}\",出现次数:44\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"86ca226e-6d79-4ca4-9097-e49827eb0d22\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"6099cd4f-f828-40c8-92c2-fa9f79a71cd5\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T02:10:40.571683257Z\"\"}\",出现次数:39\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-04"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T02:10:13Z to 2025-06-20T02:22:13Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 02:10:13+00:00 to 2025-06-20 02:22:13+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "根据我们获得的调用链数据，以下是关于 `checkoutservice` 和 `shippingservice` 间连接问题的分析总结：\n\n### 调用链数据分析\n\n1. **显著延迟**\n   - `checkoutservice` 在调用 `shippingservice` 的操作 `hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote` 显示显著延迟。\n   - 延迟倍数为 1698200.2276951058 / 9415.744961066186 ≈ 180.36，这标识出显著的延迟问题。\n\n2. **错误状态**\n   - `status_combinations` 中显示 `checkoutservice` 每次调用 `shippingservice` 均出现 DNS 解析错误。\n   - 错误状态表现为 `rpc error: code = Unavailable`, `connection error`, 并且明确指出 `lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving`。\n\n3. **错误传播路径**\n   - `frontend` 发起请求至 `checkoutservice` 时同样出现错误，表现为 `shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote`.\n   - 可确认的是该错误始于 `checkoutservice` 调用 `shippingservice`，而非 `frontend`。\n\n### 判定结果\n\n根据数据分析，错误确实指向 DNS 解析的问题，尤其是在从 `checkoutservice` 到 `shippingservice` 的连接尝试中可见。该问题与 DNS 配置有关，支持初步假设：`checkoutservice` 的 DNS 配置错误影响了其与 `shippingservice` 的连接。\n\n### JSON 输出\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Response time increased significantly during checkoutservice's calls to shippingservice, with anomaly_avg_duration much greater than normal_avg_duration.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Consistent DNS lookup failure as indicated by error message: 'lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving'.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此步骤中，我们验证了故障根因假设，发现 `checkoutservice` 和 `shippingservice` 间的 DNS 配置错误是故障的主要原因。", "log_analysis_findings": "### 第二轮信息分析\n\n最新的日志数据提取如下，所有错误日志均来自于 `frontend` 服务，并指向与 `shippingservice` 相关的 DNS 解析错误：\n\n**错误日志摘要**:\n1. **日志内容**: `\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"`\n   - 发生在 `frontend-2`, `frontend-1`, 和 `frontend-0` pods。\n   - 都是在尝试连接 `shippingservice` 时出现了 DNS lookup 失败。\n   - 关联的调用错误展现为 `failed to complete the order`.\n\n**关键标签识别**:\n- **错误类型**: `transport: Error while dialing`\n- **推测诊断**: `dns`, `lookup shippingservice`, `server misbehaving`\n\n**错误模式识别**:\n- **DNS 故障**: 由于包含 `transport: Error while dialing` 和 `lookup ...`关键词，这符合 DNS 解析问题的特征。\n- **调用方分析**: 错误日志来自 `frontend` 服务，这表明 DNS 配置问题似乎影响的是调用方（即 `checkoutservice`），而不是 `shippingservice`。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"dns\", \"lookup shippingservice\", \"server misbehaving\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"DNS lookup failure when frontend attempts to connect to shippingservice, indicating a potential configuration issue in frontend's DNS settings.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup shippingservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n根据最新信息验证，前一轮的假设得到了支持，问题出在 `frontend` 的 DNS 配置影响其连接 `shippingservice`。这一问题显然导致了服务不可用问题。在后续轮次中应集中于进一步验证并提供详细解决方案。", "metric_analysis_findings": "通过获取的指标数据，我们可以从以下异常指标中进行分析：\n\n### 异常指标数据 (摘录)\n- `checkoutservice-1` 服务的 `error_ratio` 和 `server_error_ratio` 在故障期间显著升高，变化率达到 2.0。\n- `checkoutservice-1` 的 `rrt` 和 `rrt_max` 在故障期间显著延迟，变化率分别为 1.8056 和 1.7306。\n- `shippingservice-0` 服务的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 展现显著变化，`fault_p99` 达到 31.66。\n- `tidb-tikv` 的 `region_pending` 指标略有增加，变化率为 0.159。\n\n### 假设验证\n针对\"checkoutservice has DNS configuration problems affecting connections to shippingservice\"的假设：\n\n- `checkoutservice-1` 的延迟显著上升（`rrt_max` 和 `rrt`），以及 `error_ratio` 的升高，对应了 DNS 解析错误可能导致的连接出现问题。\n- `shippingservice-0` 的 `client_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 的 spike 可能支持该假设，即 `checkoutservice-1` 在请求 `shippingservice-0` 时由于 DNS 不可达问题出现大量异常。\n- 在 `checkoutservice` 相关指标中并未发现 `pod_processes` 变化，因此不涉及 Pod 重启或生命周期异常。\n\n结合以上指标表现及逻辑推理，数据支持当前假设。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"region_pending\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in error_ratio and rrt, indicating potential DNS resolution issues affecting connectivity to shippingservice.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Fault median error_ratio at 45.22 compared to normal 0.0; rrt max spiking to 6636069.32 from normal median of 219842.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Client_error_ratio spike may indicate checkoutservice DNS configuration problems while attempting to connect.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Fault p99 client_error_ratio at 31.66 compared to normal 0.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此分析支持了当前提出的假设并提供了相应的指标佐证。"}
